long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Status: Obsolete as the Chromium project no longer uses iterations.  Feel free to uninstall.

Originally written by Andrew de los Reyes.

Version 5.0: Handle new Phase/Week instead of Iteration
Version 4.2: Add a popup & handle daylight savings
Version 4.1: Handle 3 digit iterations
Version 4.0: Rewrote iteration logic to fetch data from chromepmo.appspot.com
Version 3.3: Updated iteration # due to iteration 96 going long
Version 3.2: Updated iteration # due to iteration 85 going long
Version 3.1: Fixed URL matching
Version 3.0: Rewrote to use event/alarm system
Version 2.0: Updated to Manifest 2
